    {
      "id": "PopularPost179915",
      "post_content": "I think personally this is [Lightning Greaves](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Greaves) on crack, toned down just a tiny bit with the equip cost. But it is low enough where it really does not affect you much unlike [Argentum Armor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Argentum Armor) or [Skinwing](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Skinwing). I mean, Lightning Greaves gives your creature protection from your spells to, this lets you enchant it still, so no taking off your boots to put on armor, you can still fling it, or boost it, or do whatever you want to the creature, whereas lightning greaves would not let you.  \n7/5",
      "posted_by": "hedronMatrix",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost179915\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_post\">I think personally this is <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lightning Greaves\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Greaves\">Lightning Greaves</a> on crack, toned down just a tiny bit with the equip cost.  But it is low enough where it really does not affect you much unlike <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Argentum Armor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Argentum Armor\">Argentum Armor</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Skinwing\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Skinwing\">Skinwing</a>.  I mean, Lightning Greaves gives your creature protection from your spells to, this lets you enchant it still, so no taking off your boots to put on armor, you can still fling it, or boost it, or do whatever you want to the creature, whereas lightning greaves would not let you.<br/>7/5</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '179915'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy36194\">hedronMatrix</span>\r\n                                (7/17/2011 5:21:59 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a